{
  "id": "RAW_44101bde",
  "title": "30 分钟用 Agent 制作马年专属动图表情包，并上架微信【喂饭级教程】",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwMzE4NjU5NA==&mid=2247513514&idx=1&sn=8c3bbcd150aaa2dc98463cd9a84fe21a",
  "date": "2026-01-22 02:04:00",
  "author": " 袋鼠帝AI客栈",
  "siteName": "袋鼠帝AI客栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit;\">大家好，我是袋鼠帝。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1tcy\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">马上就要过年了，不知道大家是不是跟我一样，最近聊天斗图的时候总感觉库里的表情包不够用了。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"2\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esizm\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我就在想，不如<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">自己动手做一套？想要什么效果就做什么效果，岂不美哉。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esi7u\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这套<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">表情包还能上架到微信表情商店</span>，让你的朋友、甚至陌生人都在用你的作品。感觉比单纯发个红包有意思多了。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es52i\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可能会有朋友觉得：我也不会画画，也不会PS，更不会做动图，这门槛是不是太高了？</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1srw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">放在以前，确实是个技术活。但<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">现在，有了AI，有手就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6643454038997214\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1436\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029853\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b72f34f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6ATnGnSr5QDbZu6qsFOA0ndd52jAmVicJZT4csyUlSuAH6ibyG7UQroogg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esied\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">今天我就手把手教大家怎么用AI，从零开始花个30分钟定制一套马年专属动态表情包（对是动态的哦），包含上架到微信的全流程。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esied\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">先看看微信表情开放平台的要求，避免后续申请被驳回</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029861\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bc0c0d16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6A4nXWjmFrkfQQFQPBGqIVic4DkWib2QCTAOlia7AJialnicSPuVbzTQPiadoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko7x3yvydu\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko7x3zb12rm\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">记住！图标和封面需要透明底</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1uwn\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">好了，话不多说，我们开始</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esv1d\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">整个过程大概分为三步：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esebo\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1.设计并生成你的IP形象和马的表情包素材。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1bpx\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2.制作动态GIF并处理成微信要求的格式。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es12o6\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3.上架到微信表情开放平台。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1v7e\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们一步步来。</span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko94k7i14nl\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;1.搞定IP形象，告别抽卡&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es22hd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一步是重点，我会讲的比较详细，尽量让大家都学会并复刻</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es22hd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">做表情包得有个主角，这次我不想用袋鼠了，我想搞个自己真人的卡通形象。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9eshie\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一开始我也不知道怎么设计自己的IP形象，脑子一片空白，我相信这也是很多朋友会卡住的地方。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es12lf\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实不需要自己空想，最好的灵感往往来自模仿，我就在某书找了一些爆火的IP形象设计图。</span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"750\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029775\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4c18353&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemdsnEbqDW7Fcbs4N1EPjic4ianHmUPNF5cm4gpQWP2rME5JKBPkl60U6nA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es3q3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">得到参考图之后，以前我们可能得去琢磨怎么写提示词，什么材质啊、光影啊、渲染啊，生图的提示词是失之毫厘差之千里。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9eshci\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我比较喜欢用Gemini3 Pro帮我反推提示词</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6160188457008245\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1698\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029849\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f1f86e4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6Ahc0xoTJUohT2dHEUIcud9KHomE8V1ydXPcKKYuoraI3FgmpbNMFHPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es143p\">3D表情包提示词：</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko96i701dsa\">\n   <div style=\"width: 100%;padding: 0 12px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:10px 13px 23px 13px;width:100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 54px;height: 12px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"line-height: 12px;height: 12px;\" data-mid=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2222222222222222\" data-w=\"108\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c7aad52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F4lwaCEqic1K9Zic4kmyYGWfQb2z8mib1g3zly9wtiben3bH1RU3Xh6iaDjMR0A2hsNicR24eciah3fUvps3HFX9x4dZicQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;padding: 13px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">参考附件中的照片 &nbsp;进行 3D IP角色设计，盲盒玩具风格，泡泡玛特风格，一个可爱的Q版男孩，戴着黑色圆眼镜，黑色短发，身穿米色哈灵顿夹克和黑色T恤，浅卡其色裤子，柔软光滑的粘土质感，C4D渲染，OC渲染，干净的柔和背景，摄影棚布光，边缘光，极简主义，高细节，4k，可爱治愈的氛围，站立姿势，伸出一只手，哑光表面。</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es187r\">2D表情包提示词：</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko96q8124hq\">\n   <div style=\"width: 100%;padding: 0 12px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:10px 13px 23px 13px;width:100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 54px;height: 12px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"line-height: 12px;height: 12px;\" data-mid=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2222222222222222\" data-w=\"108\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c7aad52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F4lwaCEqic1K9Zic4kmyYGWfQb2z8mib1g3zly9wtiben3bH1RU3Xh6iaDjMR0A2hsNicR24eciah3fUvps3HFX9x4dZicQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;padding: 13px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">参考附件中的照片 &nbsp;进行2D平面插画，涂鸦风格，简单的粗轮廓线，卡哇伊角色设计，一个迷你Q版男孩，圆黑框眼镜，简单的豆豆眼，凌乱的黑色短发，穿着米色夹克，可爱的比例，极简矢量艺术，白色背景，贴纸艺术，有趣的表情，柔和的色彩，灵感来自Chiikawa风格</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9eswlr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次设计表情包我用了一个新工具，叫星流Agent，这是Liblib公司开发的一个国产AI工具。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkoslsa84ac\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkoslsak1wn0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><a href=\"https://www.xingliu.art/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xingliu.art/</a></span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4879807692307692\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1664\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029848\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4432f185&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6AIqLzicHRkC7Wt8Hya29VQicq5ASHIeT1394qWrqKlQCHNRMpE28z41Mw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es7eg\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">本来是想用Lovart的，但是有群友反应在国内访问有时候加载半天出不来，连接也不太稳定。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1pga\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">星流Agent算是Lovart的国内版，专门为国内优化，速度快，也更稳定，考虑到大家的易用性，这次我选择了星流Agent。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esjbh\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有很重要的一点是，星流Agent可以一次性批量生成多张表情不一的图片，用来做表情包效率爆表</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es114w\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">同时星流Agent里面集成了很多生图模型，我推荐选择字节的seedream4.5，这是目前国产最强的生图模型了，效果跟NanoBanana Pro接近，做表情包的话基本没差。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"880\" style=\"width: 260px;height: 260px;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029856\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=90f39b1b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6AyiciayI3PGrKUGHniaAibZ9siaZX0rpcCy80icxmzUqicQg9sw7IH7wdTblrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9ese7a\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我直接把上一步Gemini生成的提示词和一张我自己的照片发给星流Agent，让它参考生成类似的IP形象。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5067064083457526\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2684\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8db1f169&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6AQS56krL0r4gFiciaM7ml8fVG0xllGLIFHrQbZLibSAOsZQiaSkEMibEuYWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es196\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">结果很不错，它不仅理解了那个风格，还真的生成出了我想要的那种质感（生成了2D和3D）。</span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4157303370786517\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"801\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029777\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=566a6f39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemdbAMZdkSaSqBFCrO9FpIqz8B5pvw4mN0c4VdfjLUSzx0utem7KMsFFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1kx2\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">搞定了IP形象，接下来就是给马设计表情包了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9estct\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">同样的方法，找一些你觉得有趣的马的表情图作为参考。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es80f\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面是生成的一些马的表情包</span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.012924071082391\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"619\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029778\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b65204a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemdscsET2Xy7Z2BCTFCMOA3YtDDnm0LUafcxvIzfS2XibfACKZC3vUuYibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1njs\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">加上文字的版本：</span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.016260162601626\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"615\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029789\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a51ecf6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemdxBcwTpjMlsqa3x9ichsXTGS5fZgZxj4ewfsITj2sP6exp9GrggqqvFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9espkt\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">生成的效果不错，而且角色一致性保持的非常好。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1bg8\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但我发现在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">生成夸张表情的时候，有一些细节要注意：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esby\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">在生成过程中要注意这些特别夸张的表情的提示词描述，AI对于一些迪士尼风格的描述会有可爱滤镜，导致再生成一些非常夸张的表情的生成其实是很难达到我们想要的效果的，这个时候<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">提示词中就要特意强调</span>这一点。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko97tv5197x\">\n   <div style=\"width: 100%;padding: 0 12px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:10px 13px 23px 13px;width:100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 54px;height: 12px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"line-height: 12px;height: 12px;\" data-mid=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2222222222222222\" data-w=\"108\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c7aad52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F4lwaCEqic1K9Zic4kmyYGWfQb2z8mib1g3zly9wtiben3bH1RU3Xh6iaDjMR0A2hsNicR24eciah3fUvps3HFX9x4dZicQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;padding: 13px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">错误提示词：生成3D渲染，迪士尼皮克斯风格，拟人化的马，IP设计，极度详细的毛发细节，C4D渲染，Blender，8k分辨率，盲盒玩具质感。极度特写，滑稽表情，斗鸡眼，大鼻孔，张嘴露牙，凌乱的鬃毛，直视镜头，傻得可爱的脸，震惊，下巴掉下来的表情包图</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;padding: 13px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">正确提示词：3D迪士尼皮克斯风格，拟人化的马，IP角色设计，极度详细的蓬松毛发细节，C4D渲染，Blender，8k分辨率，盲盒玩具质感。(极度夸张的表情:1.5)，(丑萌:1.3)，(滑稽呆傻的脸:1.4)，(不对称的眼睛/大小眼:1.4)，一只眼眯着一只眼暴突，巨大的鼻孔扩张，嘴巴大张尖叫，舌头甩出来，双下巴，五官扭曲，滑稽荒谬，戏剧性光影。</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esqmp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">当我强调了提示词之后生成的效果就完全不一样。（左图就是没有强调的提示词生成的，而右图是强调之后的提示词生成的</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Inter, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">）</span></span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <div data-mpa-template-id=\"771\" data-mpa-category=\"模板\">\n    <div data-mpa-category=\"模板\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;grid-column-gap: 7px;\">\n       <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029779\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c910dabd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemdTdUdkgiaktDIdnc4USjoRbsxVnKnFxVRcssl7fiasNwqqDjnB9t2qjWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029780\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dd96b20c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemdd7iavTSKibQbP0AB2yWDavfSQDQiaickDPEXCiabwAib5NV27P6TQnugnsZQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1sr9\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">生成过程中，难免会遇到那种整体很完美，但某个细节有点崩的情况。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1k40\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如上面右边这张图，我其实很满意了，但马的左眼有点歪。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es524\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">按照以前的逻辑，这图就废了，得重新抽卡，可能抽很多张都抽不到这么让我心仪的构图了。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9eswnt\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">星流Agent有个邪修功能，叫Touch Edit（精准编辑）。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esdvm\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">类似一个随时待命的修图师，哪里不满意，在画面上点一下，告诉它把左眼修好，它就只动左眼，其他地方完全不变。</span></p>\n  <p data-node-view-root=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es15e5\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这效率，比反复抽卡高了很多。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1evo\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">如果需要加入文字，直接点击左侧的文字图标添加即可</span></p>\n  <p data-img-disable-preview=\"f\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5689497716894977\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1095\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029790\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a3d0261a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1AkNBmbgZAkL00ZFpVbmemd8uY5GwyGTwaIGufrqqOQYle8ljxHtJxvmnJA7PicpsY00JtVibBDVFMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es18rc\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来就是将我的ip形象和上面生成的马年表情包结合起来。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esb50\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在星流Agent引入两张参考图，然后描述你想要的效果即可，轻松搞定。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7932098765432098\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1944\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029852\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f7ede27&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1