;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esamb\">大括号中的内容可以替换成你自己的内容。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es21wa\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko9ave51mmq\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;3.上架微信&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es6l9\">在微信开发表情平台上传自己制作的表情包和GIF动图。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esn4d\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">微信表情开放平台的地址：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1teb\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><a href=\"https://sticker.weixin.qq.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://sticker.weixin.qq.com/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9153386454183267\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1004\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029840\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bc1ee20d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1DFpcsSk8jbR3Oibia7ETTR6A7BCZ0CpI2p3LSfOHh3u6IOH7nB4IA7TsRC6VT32ozf7sTPsQaCAWIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9eswic\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提交审核后，大概等个一两天，审核通过了，你就能在微信的表情商店里搜到你自己的大作啦～</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1wre\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一定要注意提交时间</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6754966887417219\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1510\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029864\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=785b6bef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1AqFuKMUyYlDKFs8MrhC1DYCcW0pibqzsVwPOFcAwJibYH3SMTt08qwoibI7JLxS3icmyfPJcEOmNQW1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mko9dk3nf34\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">「最后」</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1163\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实在有了AI之后做一套表情包，并没有我们想象的那么难。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esf3r\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">尤其是在像Lovart、星流Agent这种设计类Agent平台里面变得更简单了</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9esetz\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为它们集成了几乎所有主流AI生图、生视频工具，再加上各种工程化的\"编辑\"能力，能在享受AI强大生成能力的同时，提高获得内容的稳定性，和效率。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es13yn\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无论是那个指哪改哪的精准编辑，还是分层编辑等功能，都让我们在创作时有了更多的底气。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1nof\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且它的出图质量真的很顶（支持1k、2k、甚至4k），不管是质感还是细节，都很棒。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1wre\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">趁着离过年还有一小段时间，试试动手做一套自己的马年表情包，打开星流Agent（</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkoslsa84ac\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkoslsak1wn0\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">xingliu.art</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1wre\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">），跟着这篇教程操作，花不了多少时间，你就能拥有一套高质量的动图表情包了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es1dym\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等做好了，记得发到评论区，让大家都用起来～</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mko6v9es8vn\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提前祝大家马年大吉，马到成功！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.05em;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:1.5em;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk2dzl0722i8\" style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 0.05em;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(0, 122, 255);font-weight: bold;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk2dzl0i1gq3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\">点击关注下方账号，你将感受到一个朋克的灵魂，且每篇文章都有惊喜。</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-action-id=\"mkoqtte2o0\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe js_wx_tap_highlight\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"袋鼠帝AI客栈\" data-alias=\"masterlhm\" data-index=\"0\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/3